<script>
import AuthService from "../AuthService";

export default {
  data() {
    return {
      authenticated: false // Initially assuming user is not authenticated
    };
  },
  created() {
    this.checkAuthentication();
  },
  methods: {
    checkAuthentication() {
      // Call your authentication logic here
      // For example, calling AuthService.isAuthenticated()
      // This assumes that AuthService.isAuthenticated() returns true if authenticated, false otherwise
      this.authenticated = AuthService.isAuthenticated();
    }
  }
};
</script>
